# Project Rules

Always read and follow:

- docs/design.md
- docs/skills.md
- docs/astro.md
- docs/seo.md
- docs/product.md

Stack:
- Astro
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- date-fns
- pdf-lib
- lucide-astro

Design:
- Linear-inspired
- Dark and light mode required
- Theme switch required
- Premium SaaS aesthetic
- Minimal shadows
- Subtle borders
- Large typography
- Mobile-first

Development:
- Static pages by default
- Use Astro islands only when needed
- Keep JavaScript minimal
- No auth, database, payments, or backend unless explicitly requested

SEO:
- Tool above the fold
- Semantic HTML
- One H1 per page
- FAQ section
- Related internal links
- Fast loading